            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="apropos Mencken quote"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>apropos Mencken quote<span> (2, Funny)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~dltaylor" class="author" title="author name and user ID">dltaylor (7510) </a> | more than 3 years ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2227792&cid=36398416">(#36398416)</a></h4>
