        <div id="comment_body_36398416" class="comment-wrapper" data-points="2" data-reason="Funny">
            <div class="comment-body"><p>&#226;oeNo one in this world has ever lost money by underestimating the intelligence of the great masses of the plain people. Nor has anyone ever lost public office thereby.&#226;</p><p>Henry Louis Mencken</p></div>
